{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Then some battalion got a-- a little carry-- how do you call it-- horse, one-drawn horse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "One little carriage for one horse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they got a horse, and they got the little carriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they gave it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I think one of them was one who was getting the horse to move.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we were getting somewhere, again, to continue to get toward a point where we can go to-- to travel home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And something happened to it, again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But it was already quite a happy occasion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We could laugh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We could, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "There were Italians who killed a pig, and they roasted the pig on the road, and they gave us some-- something of it to eat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We met other people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We met, actually-- at night, we were sleeping in some haddock-- in some haystack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And there were, mingled, all people together, not only survivors and the labor, but deserters from German army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And there were two young boys who were dressed up in civilian clothing, but they must have been from the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And they were telling us they would like to come with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Could we help them to-- these guys, that they are some of, you know, our group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And we couldn't, because they were well-fed, and they spoke only German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And really, we didn't think that we could do something for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we parted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But that was-- you know, young people everywhere tried to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Those German boys, we were sorry for them because they told to us they were in the army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They couldn't do anything else but to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And they didn't know anything about concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "When we told them something, they couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
